data.description: CLOSE TO EVERYTHING .....but really. Shops, restaurants, schools, the highway....This home has close proximity to just about everything! This Cartersville Ranch home might be your perfect fit! Located in the highly desirable City School District this beautiful ranch features Newly refinished Hardwood Floors throughout and NEW Interior Paint. You’ll love the bright open floor plan. Great room complete with a beautiful Rock FIREPLACE. The kitchen has been remodeled and features beautiful white cabinets and island overlooking the great room. The backyard is perfect for entertaining and features an Outdoor kitchen/grilling area, oversized deck and a gorgeous unground pool. Situated on a spacious corner lot! This is a must see.
